dct_title_s: Survey of Berkeley Beach, Ocean County, New Jersey
dct_description_sm: This map is a traced survey of Berkeley Beach in Ocean County, the shore along Barnegat Bay and the Atlantic Ocean, and different property lots. The survey dates from November 30, 1885 and a note by J.G.P. in the lower right corner with the 1908 date. The map is surrounded by brown paper, has irregular shape, and is torn.
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
The note in the lower right corner is hard to read but contains information about the survey source map and the initials of the person who drew this copy.
